data.description: This luxurious Pool Home is fully upgraded and also located in a very desirable and family-friendly neighborhood of Cape Coral. This Immaculate and Meticulously well-maintained home has beautiful ceramic wood plank flooring throughout the main area. This High-End Kitchen features an Italian glass backsplash, stainless steel appliances, modern custom cabinets with quartz countertops, and a Brazillian custom-wood-built island. Enjoy the Huge Master bedroom that has two large Walk-in closets, dual sinks, tiled shower with a separate soaking tub to relax in. The guest bedroom features an en-suite bath with fully tiled shower. Step into the spacious living and dining room with triple panoramic sliding pocket doors that open into the Pool area with space ready for an outdoor kitchen. Enjoy the fully screened covered and paved lanai making outdoor dining & lounging with family and friends entertaining. The backyard is enclosed with a 6 ft privacy fence and mature landscaping. Live the lifestyle you dream of & Make this house your Home!
